
    A man arrested for murder and attempted murder killed
himself at the Makhado Correctional Centre.Kenneth Netsiongani was found hanging inside the cells on Wednesday
morning.Netsiongani was on parole when he got re-arrested for killing
his 5-year-old daughter and stabbed his wife.Â 
